libshout: libshout (Streaming Shoutcast Library)
libshout:
libshout: libshout is used by audio players to access streaming media servers. 
libshout: It supports Ogg Vorbis and MP3 audio streams, and can be used to
libshout: create an Internet radio station or a privately running jukebox
libshout: and many things in between. It is very versatile in that new formats 
libshout: can be added relatively easily and supports open standards for
libshout: communication and interaction.
libshout:
libshout: libshout is available from http://icecast.org
libshout:
